<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="grill-vt">grill <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡrɪl/    美 /ɡrɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(在烤架上) 烧烤；炙烤；盘问；追问：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This TV hostess is used to grilling guests on the sofa.
这位电视节目女主持人习惯于坐在沙发上盘问嘉宾。</p><footer>2018 全国改</footer></div></div>